Imagine you work for an e-commerce company. The company has a large database of customer transactions, and your task is to segment customers into different groups for targeted marketing. Which unsupervised learning technique would you use?


For customer segmentation in e-commerce, you can use clustering algorithms like K-means or hierarchical clustering.


For customer segmentation in e-commerce, you can use a dimensional reduction algorithms like PCA.

